{"type": "article", "id": 4018, "title": "*cordctrl耳机收纳棒", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-02T08:18:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233250pg3sLefz1CFAm50B.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t学计算机与经济学出身的 Mikael Schelin 很想解决始终困扰他的耳机线缠绕问题，为此他干脆自己设计了一套解决方案，便是 *cordctrl 系列。从外形上来看，*cordctrl 并无特别之处，就是一条迷你小短棍，无非是在两端开了两个小口，使得用户可以方便地将长长地耳机线绕在上面，且从两个开口处得以固定，提供多色可选，定价 9.95 欧元一根。挺贵的是吧，趁着 *cordctrl 网店维修之际，感兴趣的朋友不妨自己动手做一个吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233248IaKMQDCF0Yf96sek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233249NSJbWwsgPqxCTfrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332490MqskyJ1tW9iUjd7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233250hmFGjcQAinRYxVH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}